\&    \-v pattern           pattern not to be matched
\&    \-\-le pattern         lexical expression (same as bare pattern)
\&    \-\-re pattern         regular expression
\&    \-\-fe pattern         fixed expression
\&    \-f, \-\-file file      file contains search pattern
